selrach.bnetbuilder.model.variable
Class Potential

java.lang.Object
  selrach.bnetbuilder.model.variable.Potential

public class Potential
extends java.lang.Object

Manages a distribution over a Clique or CliqueSeparator. This is used as a starting point for the factors generated when actually constructing a JunctionTree from the Cliques
